OL,3,CInquest to be held into death of
OL,4,Cboxing champion Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of former
OL,7,Fworld boxing champion Ricky Hatton
OL,8,Fwill be held later on Friday.
OL,10,FA provisional cause of death of
OL,11,Fhanging had been given at a pre-
OL,12,Finquest hearing, when brief details
OL,13,Finto the death of the 46-year-old were
OL,14,Fmade public.
OL,16,FHatton was last seen by his family on
OL,17,FSeptember 12 when he appeared "well",
OL,18,FStockport Coroner's Court heard.
OL,20,FBut the day after, he did not attend
OL,21,Fan event as expected.
