OL,3,CInquest to be held into death of
OL,4,Cboxing champion Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FOn the morning of Sunday the 14th, his
OL,7,Fmanager Paul Speak, arrived at his
OL,8,Fhome in Hyde, Greater Manchester, to
OL,9,Ftake him to Manchester Airport to
OL,10,Fcatch a flight to Dubai.
OL,12,FMr Speak found Mr Hatton,
OL,13,F"unresponsive".
OL,15,FThe death of Hatton, a doting father
OL,16,Fand grandfather, left his family
OL,17,Fheartbroken and his army of fans
OL,18,Fstunned.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@NO]
