OL,3,CInquest to be held into death of
OL,4,Cboxing champion Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FTributes poured in from across the
OL,7,Fworld of boxing and the wider sporting
OL,8,Fcommunity for Hatton, a proud
OL,9,FMancunian and avid Manchester City
OL,10,Fsupporter.
OL,12,FLikeable, humble and a joker, Hatton,
OL,13,Falso known as "The Hitman", was
OL,14,Fregarded as a "People's Champion" and
OL,15,Fadored by thousands of fans.
OL,17,FHis all-action fighting style and down-
OL,18,Fto-earth demeanour made him one of the
OL,19,Fmost popular fighters on both sides of
OL,20,Fthe Atlantic.
OL,26,@uD@OOUuD@ZO]vD@OOUvD@aO]
