OL,3,CInquest to be held into death of
OL,4,Cboxing champion Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FHatton's family insisted the former
OL,7,Fworld champion was "in a good place",
OL,8,Fwho had plans for the future including
OL,9,Fhis bags packed for a comeback fight
OL,10,Fin Dubai in December.
OL,12,FBut Hatton had also been candid about
OL,13,Fhis mental health, struggles with
OL,14,Fdrink and drugs and past suicide
OL,15,Fattempts after he retired from the
OL,16,Fring for a second time following an
OL,17,Fill-advised comeback in 2012.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@dO]
