OL,3,CInquest to be held into death of
OL,4,Cboxing champion Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FThousands lined the streets for his
OL,7,Ffuneral at Manchester Cathedral,
OL,8,Fattended by celebrities including
OL,9,FOasis frontman Liam Gallagher, former
OL,10,FEngland and Manchester United striker
OL,11,FWayne Rooney and boxers Tyson and
OL,12,FTommy Fury.
OL,14,FHatton's inquest will begin at noon at
OL,15,FStockport Coroner's Court.
OL,17,FThe Samaritans can be called free on
OL,18,F116 123, or email them at
OL,19,Fjo@samaritans.org, or visit
OL,20,Fsamaritans.org to find your nearest
OL,21,Fbranch.
